Caroline Broue, a French journalist asked internationally acclaimed Nigerian writer if there are bookstores in her country. Adichie, in her Facebook post after the interview, said Broue was "trying to be ironic", which had not worked, and wished that the journalist "would not be publicly pilloried". Check out the full exchange between Broue and Adichie at the La Nuit Des Idees (A Night of Ideas) event.